      "content": "but it's not just about taking a break from the lab. it's like the whole foundation of who i am is gone. there's no \"me\" left without the research. i look at the future and there's just nothing there. no career, no purpose, just this massive, empty hole. it feels so heavy, like i'm constantly drowning and there's no shore in sight.",
